INGREDIENTS 2 avocados, peeled and pitted 1 cup of tomatoes, chopped ¼ cup red onion, finely chopped 2 cloves garlic, crushed ¼ cup fresh coriander, chopped 2 Tbsp lemon or lime juice 1 chili of your choice, seeded and finely chopped (optional) ½ tsp cumin Salt and black pepper to taste METHOD Mash the avocados in a bowl to your preferred consistency. Mix the tomato, onion, garlic, cumin, coriander, lime juice and chili pepper into the avocado. Season with salt and pepper. 